<!-- Slide 8: Switch Out -->
<div class="slide-container" id="slide8">
    <h2 class="slide-title">
        <span lang="en">VI. Operational: Switch-Out Mechanism</span>
        <span lang="id">VI. Operasional: Mekanisme Switch-Out</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="content-area">
        <div class="two-column" style="gap: 40px; align-items: center;">
            <div>
                <h3 style="color: #d97706;"><span lang="en">Inactive Participant Policy</span><span lang="id">Kebijakan Peserta Tidak Aktif</span></h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <span lang="en">To ensure flexibility and maintain a stable number of active seats, we apply a "Seat Model" where the insurer keeps the seat, but the participant occupying it can be replaced.</span>
                    <span lang="id">Untuk menjaga fleksibilitas dan kestabilan jumlah seat aktif, kami menerapkan "Model Seat" di mana asuransi memiliki kursi, namun peserta yang mengisinya dapat diganti.</span>
                </p>
                <div class="tile centered" style="background-color: #fff7ed; border-color: #d97706;">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-user-slash" style="font-size: 40px; color: #d97706; margin-bottom: 15px;"></i>
                    <h4 style="margin: 0; color: #9a3412; font-size: 18px; margin-top: 10px;">
                        <span lang="en">"Inactive" Definition</span>
                        <span lang="id">Definisi "Tidak Aktif"</span>
                    </h4>
                    <p style="font-size: 16px; margin-top: 5px;">
                        <span lang="en">30 consecutive days with zero logs and no coaching interaction.</span>
                        <span lang="id">30 hari berturut-turut tanpa log (data) dan tanpa interaksi coaching.</span>
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tile blue-accent">
                <div class="bullet-list">
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-rotate"></i>
                            <strong><span lang="en">Eligibility:</span><span lang="id">Kelayakan:</span></strong>
                            <br><span lang="en">1 replacement allowed per seat per year.</span>
                            <span lang="id">1 kali penggantian diizinkan per seat per tahun.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li style="margin-top: 20px;">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice"></i>
                            <strong><span lang="en">Billing Effect:</span><span lang="id">Efek Billing:</span></strong>
                            <br><span lang="en">Inactive billing stops from next cycle (21st). Replacement billing starts only after successful onboarding.</span>
                            <span lang="id">Tagihan tidak aktif berhenti siklus berikutnya (tgl 21). Tagihan pengganti mulai setelah onboarding sukses.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
